summary: This mod adds in Skyrim sword of King Llane Wrynn from Warcraft movie.
descriptionHtml:
WHAT IS IT

This mod adds in Skyrim sword of King Llane Wrynn from Warcraft movie.

WHERE TO FIND

A sword is on the table in the Dragon Reach in Whiterun.

Weapons settings a little weaker than the Daedric.

Textures Resolution 2K
In screenshots used Tetrachromatic ENB

I HOPE YOU LIKE MY WORK!

In the future, I plan to make a high-quality paladin Tier 6 armor from the WoW game. I'm working on it when there is free time, I hope to post it in February or March.
author: malsbury
